  "baseRefName": "main",
  "body": "## Summary\n\nAdds a self-contained Dealix **Commercial Launch OS**: a deterministic, stdlib-only, founder-review draft factory plus the supporting commercial, delivery, and media/social documentation. It satisfies the golden rule end-to-end and proves it with tests:\n\n> **AI drafts and ranks. The founder reviews and approves. The system never sends externally.**\n\nThis is built as a new, isolated namespace (`config/commercial_*`, `scripts/commercial_*`, `docs/commercial-launch/`, `docs/media-social-os/`) and does **not** modify the existing production commercial systems, API, or the Next.js web build.\n\n## Includes\n\n- **First 5 verticals** — facilities management, contracting & project controls, real estate ops, legal & professional services (privacy-first), consulting/training/B2B — each a deep playbook in `docs/commercial-launch/verticals/`.\n- **400+ daily draft factory** — `scripts/commercial_generate_400_drafts.py` (175 cold email / 100 follow-up / 75 LinkedIn manual / 50 website-form), every draft approval-gated and scored (quality / compliance / fit / priority).\n- **Founder Review Queue** — `founder_review.{md,csv}`, `top_50_priority.md`, rejected/needs-research splits, daily metrics, batch manifest → `outputs/commercial_launch/<date>/` (git-ignored; regenerated).\n- **Safety audit** — `scripts/commercial_safety_audit.py` scans for real send-code and bad flag states and verifies the batch; **PASS**.\n- **Quality + compliance gates** — banned-phrase, opt-out, single-offer, misleading-subject, and privacy-first (legal) enforcement.\n- **SAR offer ladder** + pricing, sales messaging (AR/EN), objections, discovery, proposal/one-pager, delivery OS, metrics dashboard, external go-live requirements, lead-intake/CRM schema.\n- **Media & Social OS** — 30-day bilingual content calendar (plan only), platform OS docs, press kit, ads **planning** only; `auto_publish=false` everywhere.\n- **3 GitHub Actions** — `commercial-draft-factory`, `media-social-calendar`, `site-commercial-verify`; all `permissions: contents: read`, no secrets, artifact-only, no deploy.\n- **README** — corrected clone URL to `Dealix-sa/dealix` and added a Commercial Launch OS section.\n\n## Safety\n\n- No external sending. No SMTP, WhatsApp outbound, LinkedIn automation, or website auto-submit anywhere — enforced by `commercial_safety_audit.py` and `test_commercial_no_external_send.py`.\n- No secrets, no API keys, no browser automation, no scraping. Seed leads are synthetic with no personal contact fields.\n- Every draft: `send_allowed=false`, `external_send_blocked=true`, `requires_founder_approval=true`, `no_auto_send=true`.\n\n## Tests run (local)\n\n- `pytest` over the 10 new files → **42 passed**.\n- `python scripts/commercial_generate_400_drafts.py --target 400` → 400 drafts, 378 into review, 22 compliance-rejected, 0 quality-rejected.\n- `python scripts/commercial_safety_audit.py` → **PASS** (400 checked).\n- `python scripts/commercial_launch_readiness.py` → **READY**.\n- `make env-check` → ✅ ; `make api-contract-check` → ✅.\n- `make security-smoke` → fails **only on pre-existing** fixtures/docs (`tests/test_*`, `docs/ops/*`); **none of the new files are flagged**.\n\n## Scope notes (honest)\n\n- The marketing site (`apps/web`) already ships SEO (robots/sitemap/manifest/JSON-LD/OG, bilingual). To avoid risking the production build, the site was **not rewritten**; a `site-commercial-verify` workflow hard-gates commercial readiness + SEO presence and runs the web build as a non-blocking informational job. See `docs/site-launch/99_SITE_LAUNCH_REPORT.md`.\n- No new send endpoints were added to the API.\n\n## Go / No-Go\n\n**GO:** site launch (existing site), draft generation, founder review, media planning, paid diagnostics, discovery calls, proposals.\n\n**NO-GO:** automated sending, cold WhatsApp, LinkedIn automation, bulk email, website auto-submit, paid ads without tracking/legal review, processing sensitive data before agreement.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01JdKfpPmB2gQBkeAa7xXPw9\n\n---\n_Generated by [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code/session_01JdKfpPmB2gQBkeAa7xXPw9)_",
